$$ {\text{MVO}}_{2} = a \times {\text{PVA}} + b $$\end{document}where a is the slope coefficient and b is unloaded MVO2. PVA consists of the external mechanical work EW (J/beat) within the contraction cycle and the potential energy PE (J/beat) 4\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
