Ventricular pressure–volume loopsThe following symbols are used in Eq. 5:
ppeakS (Pa) maximal value of the systolic ventricular pressure
ppED (Pa) end-diastolic ventricular pressure
VED (m3) end-diastolic ventricular volume
VES (m3) end-systolic ventricular volume
Vo (m3) ventricular volume at zero pressure (point of intersection on the volume axis, see Fig. 1).
